From 9c99fd35cbe57b7b9659c3d1f29b932b7015ed59 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Matthew Bucci <mtbucci@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Apr 2026 09:17:19 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] Qwen3.5 MoE text-only CausalLM integration

- Add Qwen3_5ForCausalLM / Qwen3_5MoeForCausalLM wrapper classes with
  lm_head + logits_processor returning LogitsProcessorOutput
- Rename backbone classes to Qwen3_5Model / Qwen3_5MoeModel
- Update ConditionalGeneration classes to reference renamed backbones
- Update qwen3_5_mtp.py to use Qwen3_5Model backbone
- Add mrope position handling in CausalLM forward
- Extend _bind_packed_weight_loaders for AWQ attrs (qweight/scales/qzeros)
- Fix _get_split_sizes_for_param for PackedvLLMParameter pack factor
- Fix FusedMoE _load_w13/_load_w2 TP overflow for CT scale/zero tensors
- Add AWQ MoE process_weights_after_loading diagnostic logging

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
